%^BOLD%^-=%^YELLOW%^Creation Domain%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

Drawing upon the desire to create, rather than destroy, the creation domain allows the cleric to make useful items to help them on their journey.

Clerics with the Creation Domain gain the following benefits:
- A +1 bonus to caster level when casting conjuration school spells.
- Minions summoned with monster summoning spells gain +10 spell damage resistance

The creation domain contains the following spells:

Minor Creation, Glitterdust, Secret Chest, Instant Summons, Mages Sword

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Edea

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
